'''Steam大奖'''是[[Valve|Valve]]旗下平台[[Steam|Steam]]于2016年开始，每年举办的游戏大奖评选活动，获奖游戏均由Steam用户选出。

== 介绍 ==
Steam大奖分为两个阶段，第一阶段，Valve提供了多个可选奖项供玩家选择，Valve会根据最终数量评选出前五名获奖游戏，随后将这些提名结果提交给Steam用户，由用户在这五名获奖游戏之中再次选择。随后，Valve宣布获胜者。<ref name="pgc nom">{{Cite web|title=Valve reveals Steam Awards nominees|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/valve-reveals-steam-awards-nominees/|accessdate=2016-12-22|author=Donneley|date=2016-12-22|first=Joe|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222135810/http://www.pcgamer.com/valve-reveals-steam-awards-nominees/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 游戏提名和投票时间在Steam每年的秋季和冬季假期活动同时进行。 <ref name="poly">{{Cite web|title=Valve introduces Steam Awards, chosen by the community|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/11/23/13734480/steam-awards-2016-autumn-sale|accessdate=2016-12-31|author=Sarkar|date=2016-11-23|first=Samit|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101090943/http://www.polygon.com/2016/11/23/13734480/steam-awards-2016-autumn-sale|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="2019:">{{Cite web|title=The Steam Autumn Sale has begun, Steam Award nominations are now being taken|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/the-steam-autumn-sale-has-begun-steam-award-nominations-are-now-being-taken/|accessdate=2019-11-26|author=Chalk|first=Andy|work=PC Gamer|archive-date=2019-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191127190144/https://www.pcgamer.com/the-steam-autumn-sale-has-begun-steam-award-nominations-are-now-being-taken/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

